## Future Scope & Enhancements

### Planned Upgrades
1.  **Backend Integration**: Connect to a robust backend (Node.js/Express + MongoDB) for real-time data sync.
2.  **Real-Time Video**: Integrate WebRTC (e.g., Agora or Twilio) for actual video consultations.
3.  **Payment Gateway**: Integrate Stripe/Razorpay for processing consultation fees.
4.  **IoT Integration**: Connect with wearables (Apple Watch, Fitbit) to auto-sync vitals.

### Conclusion
Sarthi AI represents a significant step towards accessible digital healthcare. By leveraging modern web technologies and Generative AI, it creates a seamless personalized healthcare experience, promising to reduce the burden on traditional healthcare systems while empowering users.
